{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1698-11_085", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Rupture"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", novembre 1698 [tome 11], p. 85-93."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je ne sçay, Madame, si vous trouverez qu’il en faille croire l’Auteur des Vers que je vous envoye. Les sermens qu’on fait de ne plus aimer sont souvent fort inutiles, & c’est dans ce temps qu’on est quelquefois le plus amoureux. Lisez cependant, cet ouvrage le merite. Il est de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " Mahuet de Reims."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "RUPTURE."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "J’ay vaincu mon Vainqueur, j’ay forcé ma prison,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "J’ay du joug de l’amour affranchy ma raison,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et las de soupirer pour l’ingrate Climene,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "À moy-mesme à la fin mon destin me ramene."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Assez, & trop long-temps, son insensible coeur"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "A fait sentir au mien une injuste rigueur."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’un autre plus constant aille adorer ses charmes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Etaler ses langueurs, & répandre des larmes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’il tâche par ses pleurs d’attendrir un Rocher,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Que tous les miens, helas ! n’ont jamais pû toucher ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Que la comblant toujours de pompeuses loüanges,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Il vante sa beauté plus que celle des Anges ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Ou qu’un amour pressant, animant ses discours ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Il trouve ce moment qui m’échapa toujours ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Je n’en suis point jaloux, & de cette amourette"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "J’entendrois sans chagrin raisonner sa Musette,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Que Climene le souffre à l’ombre d’un Ormeau,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour chanter ses faveurs enfler son chalumeau,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[19]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[19]/text()[1]", "text": "J’y consens, je puis voir desormais sans envie,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[20]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[20]/text()[1]", "text": "Climene avec Lycas passer toute sa vie,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[21]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[21]/text()[1]", "text": "Et mon cœur libre enfin d’un nœud qui l’a charmé,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[22]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[22]/text()[1]", "text": "Croit dans ce calme heureux n’avoir jamais aimé."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[23]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[23]/text()[1]", "text": "En vain pour renflamer ce cœur tout plein de glace,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[24]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[24]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu voudrois dans le tien me donner une place,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[25]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[25]/text()[1]", "text": "Il est trop inconstant pour arrester le mien ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[26]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[26]/text()[1]", "text": "Et quand on aime tout, l’on n’aime jamais rien."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[27]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[27]/text()[1]", "text": "Autrefois, il est vray, ma boüillante jeunesse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[28]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[28]/text()[1]", "text": "Me fit avec ardeur rechercher ta tendresse."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[29]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[29]/text()[1]", "text": "Helas ! trop ébloüy de ta fiere beauté,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[30]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[30]/text()[1]", "text": "Je perdis ma raison, avec ma liberté."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[31]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[31]/text()[1]", "text": "Quels charmes mon amour attachoit à ma peine"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[32]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[32]/text()[1]", "text": "J’adorois mes liens, j’idolâtrois mes chaisnes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[33]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[33]/text()[1]", "text": "Et mes yeux sur les tiens sans relâche attachez,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[34]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[34]/text()[1]", "text": "J’expliquois de mon cœur les sentimens cachez."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[35]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[35]/text()[1]", "text": "Je n’aspirois alors qu’au bonheur de te plaire ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[36]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[36]/text()[1]", "text": "Je te sacrifiay mon aimable Bergere,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[37]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[37]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais l’injuste mépris dont tu sçais m’outrager,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[38]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[38]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne me punit que trop d’avoir osé changer,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[39]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[39]/text()[1]", "text": "Si quelquefois mes yeux s’éloignoient de tes charmes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[40]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[40]/text()[1]", "text": "Mes yeux, mes tristes yeux se noyoient dans les larmes."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[41]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[41]/text()[1]", "text": "Témoins de mon amour, infortunez Ruisseaux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[42]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[42]/text()[1]", "text": "Combien de fois mes pleurs ont ils grossy vos eaux ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[43]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[43]/text()[1]", "text": "Plus touchez de mes maux que l’ingrate Climene,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[44]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[44]/text()[1]", "text": "Daphnis, m’avez-vous dit, que ne romps tu ta chaisne ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[45]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[45]/text()[1]", "text": "Trop malheureux Berger, va, cesse d’estre amant,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[46]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[46]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Sexe est comme nous, & tourne à tout moment."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[47]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[47]/text()[1]", "text": "Souvent le Rossignol sous un sombre feüillage,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[48]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[48]/text()[1]", "text": "A joint à mes soupirs son languissant ramage ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[49]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[49]/text()[1]", "text": "Et brûlé d’un amour qu’il exprimoit trop bien,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[50]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[50]/text()[1]", "text": "J’ay vû dans son tourment la peinture du mien."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[51]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[51]/text()[1]", "text": " Nonchalamment couchez dans de fertiles plaines,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[52]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[52]/text()[1]", "text": "Partageant avec moy le fardeau de mes peines"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[53]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[53]/text()[1]", "text": "Helas ! petits Moutons, à mes gemissemens,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[54]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[54]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous mêliez tout le jour vos tristes bêlemens."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[55]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[55]/text()[1]", "text": "Climene seule alors trop fiere de ses charmes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[56]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[56]/text()[1]", "text": "Dédaignoit mes soupirs, triomphoit de mes larmes."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[57]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[57]/text()[1]", "text": " Mais enfin je respire, un genereux effort"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[58]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[58]/text()[1]", "text": "Vient d’affranchir mon coeur d’un si rigoureux sort."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[59]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[59]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vais vivre content, & ma mourante vie"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[60]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[60]/text()[1]", "text": "De soupirs, & de pleurs ne sera plus suivie,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[61]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[61]/text()[1]", "text": " Vous, tendres Arbrisseaux, pardonnez à ma main,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[62]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[62]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui d’un fer trop pointu déchira vostre sein,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[63]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[63]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous ne vangez que trop vos profondes blessures,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[64]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[64]/text()[1]", "text": "(D’un feu trop tard éteint les vivantes Peintures)"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[65]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[65]/text()[1]", "text": "Helas ! j’ay beau changer vous retracez toujours,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[66]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[66]/text()[1]", "text": "Ces Vers, signes honteux de mes tristes amours,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[67]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[67]/text()[1]", "text": "L’infortuné Daphnis soupire pour Climene,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[68]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[68]/text()[1]", "text": "Dont le cœur est plus dur que celuy de ce Chesne,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[69]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[69]/text()[1]", "text": " Mais que m’importe enfin qu’en tant de lieux gravé"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[70]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[70]/text()[1]", "text": "Son nom malgré le temps soit toujours conservé,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[71]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[71]/text()[1]", "text": "Si ce nom, où ma flamme attacha trop de gloire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[72]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[72]/text()[1]", "text": "Va, pour n’y plus rentrer, sortir de ma memoire ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[73]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[73]/text()[1]", "text": " Tarissez donc, mes yeux, vous ne pleurerez plus."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[74]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[74]/text()[1]", "text": "Et toy, qui t’épuisant en regrets superflus,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[75]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[75]/text()[1]", "text": "Devenois du chagrin la victime & la proye,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[76]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[76]/text()[1]", "text": "Mon coeur, consacrons nous desormais à la joye."}]}]}]}]}